OL,5, An investigation has been launched     
OL,6, after claims of "bullying and a toxic  
OL,7, culture" at publicly-funded            
OL,8, Welsh-language channel S4C.            
OL,10,FThe independent external investigation 
OL,11,Fcomes after the claims were made by a  
OL,12,Funion representing staff.              
OL,14,FA letter written by the Bectu union    
OL,15,Fdescribed a "a culture of fear" within 
OL,16,Fthe organisation.                      
OL,18,FS4C said it has decided to appoint a   
OL,19,Flaw firm to undertake an independent   
OL,20,Finvestigation into concerns raised.    
